    "name": "Lost Lands",
    "steam_appid": 2345940,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345940/extras/503c3cd98743b34fc60092c3ec751f4d.avif?t=1768205850\" width=616 height=198 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345940/extras/b76675ee94d608136a669e7e51f11a43.webp?t=1768205850\" width=164 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是第一个踏入这片失落之地的人。是时候建造、探索和发现了！这片奇妙的古老世界蕴藏着许多谜团，而你将是揭开它们的人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345940/extras/8afd26bc596529426905b936da7108fb.webp?t=1768205850\" width=124 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345940/extras/860c589bd825c07a8ca800001b0c3772.poster.avif?t=1768205850\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345940/extras/860c589bd825c07a8ca800001b0c3772.webm?t=1768205850\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345940/extras/860c589bd825c07a8ca800001b0c3772.mp4?t=1768205850\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你从一个孤独的篝火开始，周围是一片未被探索的土地。揭开周围的区域，发现新的建造地点、可收集的资源、可探索的遗迹、可研究的符文石……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345940/extras/5d6764c93e21098ea878cd5952f1be83.webp?t=1768205850\" width=315 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345940/extras/b2e1930e3598ee8ddc6c48ef32608856.poster.avif?t=1768205850\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345940/extras/b2e1930e3598ee8ddc6c48ef32608856.webm?t=1768205850\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345940/extras/b2e1930e3598ee8ddc6c48ef32608856.mp4?t=1768205850\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在失落之地中的每一座建筑都有其功能，许多建筑开启了与世界互动的新方式。建造一座伐木工小屋——现在你可以砍伐森林地块获取木材，或清除挡路的荆棘。还有更多其他功能。随着你的扩展，你的工具带也会不断丰富。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345940/extras/c57c012c8121ca12513b946e8a3487c1.webp?t=1768205850\" width=509 height=61 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345940/extras/c954d3181620d22a01a630904f30341d.poster.avif?t=1768205850\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345940/extras/c954d3181620d22a01a630904f30341d.webm?t=1768205850\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345940/extras/c954d3181620d22a01a630904f30341d.mp4?t=1768205850\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你开始游戏时选择的每位酋长都有自己独特的定居点建设方式——拥有独特的建造树、天赋和目标。利用他们的优势来适应你所处的各种情况！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345940/extras/4f61e107d7464519a2f14782ef6ad7cd.webp?t=1768205850\" width=315 height=61 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345940/extras/facb911bbf172a8c7d0ecb2577d3e429.poster.avif?t=1768205850\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345940/extras/facb911bbf172a8c7d0ecb2577d3e429.webm?t=1768205850\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345940/extras/facb911bbf172a8c7d0ecb2577d3e429.mp4?t=1768205850\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一次游戏都有独特的地形、环境和气候！随着昼夜交替，季节也会更替，每个季节都会为你的城镇和周围环境带来变化。每个季节还伴随着其特有的正常或有时奇异的天气条件。为严酷的冬季做好准备，并利用这些条件为你所用。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345940/extras/257e374d34dc9e285950386fe9e31556.avif?t=1768205850\" width=572 height=152 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无需担心。你不会输掉游戏。拿上一杯热可可，裹上毯子，放松身心，享受这个过程。</p>",
